Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責本地區偵查任務的也是Pixy小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難纏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 米歇爾學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偵查中確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該F-217小行星帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天頂星人的古代戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:36.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為預定航線上的偵查任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍隊負責
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動新統合軍手續煩瑣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成本也高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士氣和配合反而更低
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:50.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們這種民間軍事組織會受重用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的資本主義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流了七千餘年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默無聞地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圈內三個熱源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnArial}Queadluun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都是模擬彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怯場 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是七號選手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌·李小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:43.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是蘭歌·李
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭姆 有架在追你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-4 擊落一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他駕駛Battroid也那麼上畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,655)\fs24}人形模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:33.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 告訴過他打完馬上找下個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說李小姐的特長是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李小姐接下來要演唱的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家耳熟能詳的那首傳說歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和某人年輕時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛 你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才會受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫妮卡真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是模擬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De-Fold反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Victor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11年前第117次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大規模調查船團遇難事件知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:38.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捲入Fold斷層死了上千人那次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:47.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上他們是被Vajra所害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:53.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 我們只裝了模擬彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:05.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們偵查任務中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:23.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝著實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:34.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後摔倒的也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看蘭歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審查前 不發表意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:49.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位是9號選手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達·美玲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:06.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們為什麼被授予高價的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了生還
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧那種古董還能用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天頂星人的武器是優秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算過幾千年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕對不會發生機械故障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 你看他如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢又魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有天份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你們今後的教導了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝協助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭·格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早乙女訓練生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達最終入隊考核的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈 本年度Macross Frontier小姐是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(830,450)}{\frz-90}{\fn@黑体}運輸包場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.82,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,250)}{\fs50}S
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.82,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,295)}{\fs50}M
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.82,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,340)}{\fs50}S
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下學校和公司裏都能一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚著臉皮入隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始是我們的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹 小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葛蘭·格蘭上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:29.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人化後 上尉不知為何會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺傳因子不夠聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 葛蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:39.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我稍微高那麼一丁點就得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾 今天給你點顏色看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:47.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你這小人往哪跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘娘招牌菜 金槍魚饅頭要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這次的Macross小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:07.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉沒能看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 一開始就很勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在大家面前不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒這天份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多會加入SMS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會很辛苦吧 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是次機遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:38.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想傳達給大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:49.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:58.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:09.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙竟然能鬧到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:18.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:55.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被謝麗爾隨意擺佈的阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌也在尋找阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:24:01.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人在意想不到的地方遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Star Date
